# Testing Rules

## Backend (Pytest)

- Health and API tests in `tests/backend/`
- **Required:** Integration tests for all valid status transitions and representative invalid ones (`tests/integration/test_status_transitions.py`)
- Use isolated DB per test (in-memory SQLite)

## Frontend (Vitest + RTL)

- Test user-facing behavior, not implementation details
- Cover: user selector, error display, major views (list, detail, create)

## Before Claiming Done

- Run `pytest ../../tests -v` from `src/backend/`
- Run `npm test` from `src/frontend/`
- Update `test-results.md`
